root: ^Why Helvezia, what are you doing here?
^You will give yourself ze attack of heart!
^But you’re so old. How is this even possible?!
^Now hold ze phone for a second! I-
^This isn’t about you Bhomas, my god.
^Bhomas, oh my god, would you pipe the fuck down!
^I don’t have ze pipe, Helvezia listen!
^Obviously, I’ve regretted sleeping with you the second we started.
^This is our child and we will raise it together!
